      • options

        ChangeFeedProcessor.BuilderDefinition options(ChangeFeedProcessorOptions changeFeedProcessorOptions)
        Sets the ChangeFeedProcessorOptions to be used.

        Unless specifically set the default values that will be used are: - maximum items per page or FeedResponse: 100 - lease renew interval: 17 seconds - lease acquire interval: 13 seconds - lease expiration interval: 60 seconds - feed poll delay: 5 seconds - maximum scale count: unlimited

        Parameters:
        changeFeedProcessorOptions - the change feed processor options to use.
        Returns:
        current Builder.

      • handleChanges

        ChangeFeedProcessor.BuilderDefinition handleChanges(Consumer<List<CosmosItemProperties>> consumer)
        Sets a consumer function which will be called to process changes.
        Parameters:
        consumer - the consumer of ChangeFeedObserver to call for handling the feeds.
        Returns:
        current Builder.

      • leaseContainer

        Returns:
        current Builder.
